    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Executive Sport Sedan is a remarkable example of a well-cared-for professional vehicle. The exterior is finished in a Deep Sapphire Metallic that retains a deep, lustrous shine; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, barely-visible scratch near the rear wheel well, the body remains straight and free of any significant dents. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of premium cream leather and brushed aluminum accents. The upholstery has been kept in a smoke-free environment and treated regularly, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. Every feature, from the heated seats and panoramic sunroof to the advanced driver-assistance suite, is in perfect working order. Mechanically, this car is top-tier. It comes with a complete service history from authorized dealerships, including a recent major service that covered fluid flushes and a spark plug replacement. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It drives smoothly, shifts effortlessly, and offers the peace of mind that only comes from a vehicle that has been genuinely loved by its previous owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
